metadata.name: Kabikinase Pws 1500000units vial 1500 IU Injection powder for solution

clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For the treatment of acute evolving transmural myocardial infarction pulmonary embolism deep vein thrombosis arterial thrombosis or emolism and occlusion of arteriovenous cannulae

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Streptokinase creates an active complex which promotes the cleavage of the Arg Val bond in plasminogen to form the proteolytic enzyme plasmin Plasmin in turn degrades the fibrin matrix of the thrombus thereby exerting its thrombolytic action This helps eliminate blood clots or arterial blockages that cause myocardial infarction
